Supreme Court Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg has died. She was 87.

"We're going to spend a lot of time talking about it between now and November," says @JeffreyToobin. "Today... the right thing to do is to talk about what a giant this very tiny woman was." https://t.co/dqmPVB4Vws https://t.co/CDcJcqqb7E
